cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it describes a method for annotating corpora with new tagsets using existing taggers and lexical resources. It also involves machine learning, which is a common technique used in NLP research. The paper could also be relevant to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) due to the use of machine learning and the combination of existing resources.
